- Directory Structure

	lib: library files
	scripts: compilation scripts
	src: source file directory

- Which source file to edit?
	./src/DataReplicator.bsv
	./src/FixedAdder.bsv
	./src/FixedMultiplier.bsv

- How to compile the code?
  for data replicator
	> make ReplicatorTest

  for fixed point adder
  > make AdderTest

  for fixed point multiplier
  > make MultiplierTest

- How to run the testbench?
	> make run

- How to clean up codebase?
	> make clean

